  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Cook the noodles according to package instructions.",
    "In a large wok or pan, heat 1 tbsp of peanut oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced cabbage, carrots, and bell peppers, cooking until tender, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked noodles, grated ginger, garlic powder, lemon juice, and sesame seeds (if using), and stir-fry for 1-2 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and roast in the oven for 10-12 minutes, or until crispy on top.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions (if using)."
